t between environmental preservation and the exploitation of natural resources to sustain our modern society.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Okt 2021) 7aNATURE / Environmental Conservation & Protection.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780292761445423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780292761445/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK